flowchart TD
    A([Start]) --> B["Apply @trace_flow()<br/>Decorator"]
    B --> C[Instantiate PocketFlow Nodes]
    C --> D[Begin Flow Execution]
    D --> E["Node: prep phase"]
    E --> F["Langfuse: log prep<br/>inputs + timing"]
    F --> G{prep OK?}
    G -->|Error| H["Langfuse: record<br/>exception + metadata"]
    H --> Z([End])
    G -->|Success| I["Node: exec phase"]
    I --> J["Langfuse: log exec<br/>inputs + timing"]
    J --> K{exec OK?}
    K -->|Error| L["Langfuse: record<br/>exception + metadata"]
    L --> Z
    K -->|Success| M["Node: post phase"]
    M --> N["Langfuse: log post<br/>inputs + timing"]
    N --> O{post OK?}
    O -->|Error| P["Langfuse: record<br/>exception + metadata"]
    P --> Z
    O -->|Success| Q["Langfuse: flush<br/>trace span"]
    Q --> R{More nodes?}
    R -->|Yes| E
    R -->|No| S["Langfuse: finalize<br/>distributed trace"]
    S --> Z